--
-- Table structure for table `cms_email_template`
--

CREATE TABLE `cms_email_template` (
  `id` int(10) NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `content` text CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `parameters` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `config` text CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `data` text CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `id_key` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime NOT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

--
-- Dumping data for table `cms_email_template`
--

--
-- Table structure for table `cms_layout`
--

CREATE TABLE `cms_layout` (
  `id` int(5) NOT NULL,
  `token` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `theme` varchar(15) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(150) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `type_group` varchar(150) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `slug` varchar(150) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `type` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `content` text CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `data` text CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

--
-- Table structure for table `cms_log`
--

CREATE TABLE `cms_log` (
  `id` bigint(20) NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(150) NOT NULL,
  `admin_id` int(10) NOT NULL,

  `datas` text NOT NULL,
  `ips` varchar(250) NOT NULL,

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `cms_menu`
--

CREATE TABLE `cms_menu` (
  `id` int(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(120) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `slug` varchar(120) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `parent_id` int(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `description` text CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `data` text CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(3) UNSIGNED NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `type` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT 'category',
  `icon` varchar(60) CHARACTER SET utf8 DEFAULT NULL,
  `featured` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `order` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `is_default` tinyint(3) UNSIGNED NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

--
-- Dumping data for table `cms_menu`
--

INSERT INTO `cms_menu` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `parent_id`, `description`, `data`, `status`, `type`, `icon`, `featured`, `order`, `is_default`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES

-- Table structure for table `cms_migrations`

  `id` int(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL,
  `migration` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `batch` int(11) NOT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `cms_miss_room`
--

CREATE TABLE `cms_miss_room` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `slug` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `title` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `description` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `content` text NOT NULL,
  `admin_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `difficult` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 5,
  `image` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `order_index` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `time` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `config` text NOT NULL,
  `views` bigint(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `updated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp()
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- Dumping data for table `cms_miss_room`
--
